Let’s Party
Fox’s Lounge in South Miami is the perfect spot to host birthdays, anniversaries, and other milestone events.
Nostalgic and unpretentious, Fox’s offers a mix of classic American dishes and strong, expertly crafted cocktails.
To host your event at Fox’s Lounge, please fill out the form below and we will get back to you shortly!
